<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Gave one of these to my pet yesterday. Combined with intensify death, this thing was going off every 6 seconds or less. After awhile, I dumped the group and started soloing. I rarely had to fear! The mobs were just standing there getting their asses beat! This is a great pet weapon, and possibly the best. Just imagine 4 necro pets dual wielding these on a mob. You might get sick of that laugh (but I doubt it ;)</font></td></tr></table>
