<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: It is me</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-20 14:20:53</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have been visiting Black Burrow to help out some friends and there is a new mob in the clover room.  It is call Split-Paw Commander.  Both times we killed him he dropped the gnoll hide larit.  He does not spawn in the normal room but in the left hand leaf of the clover.  It seems he spawns 1:6 or so.  He trades off with a Gnoll Shaman, Gnoll Commander, and an Elite Guard.  Not sure if a normal guard will also spawn there.  He was Green to me at 29.  And he was quite a bit harder then the normal Gnoll Commander.  I would say almost twice the hits points or so.</font></td></tr></table>
