<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Miradi</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-29 09:00:10</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I was just passing Blackburrow tonight, was bored and decided to wander around in there since I have not been there in a while.  In the commander room, I was killing commanders and after my third kill, the Split Paw Commander spawned.  Not only did he drop the Gnoll Hide Lariat, he USED it!  I was stunned for half the battle.  He cons green to me at lvl 20 but he forced me to feign death and heal three times before I could take him down.  A very nice weapon, I must say.  I can't use it since I am a monk, but I'll give it to my ranger friend as a present for their 25th. =)</font></td></tr></table>
