<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Here is a topic that I never thought I would come back to.  SPlitpaw<BR>
I am a 41 ogre warrior on rallos zek.  Lately I have been researching <BR>
several options to replace my 2 yaks.  I read a thread about<BR>
the moss covered twig with stats of like 3/11 or somthing like that<BR>
(not positive). There were many posts about how powerful that<BR>
was since 45+ warriors get a damage bonus.  With a high dexterity,<BR>
I can possibly see these whips being of great use on mobs such as wurms,<BR>
frost giants, and other hard hitting mobs.  After all, lets face it,<BR>
warriors wont be soloing after level 25.  So the stun on these whips could<BR>
really save the cleric some healing.  And give those shaman, necro, <BR>
and druid DOT's some time to do their thing.  Also, stun is a great taunt,<BR>
so those wizards can have at em..and the mob will still hate the warrior.<BR>
This tactic remains to be tested..i'm gonna get some whips tonight<BR>
and try it out.</font></td></tr></table>
